headline: Is ServiceNow Stock Underperforming the Nasdaq?
summary: Despite its underperformance relative to the Nasdaq Composite in the past year, Wall Street maintains an enthusiastic outlook on ServiceNow’s future expansion prospects.

headline: Is Uber Technologies Stock Outperforming the S&P 500?
summary: With Uber Technologies outperforming the S&P 500 over the past year, analysts continue to hold a decidedly bullish view on the company’s future prospects.
